Life management CLI - unified interface for personal automation.

Commands:
  bank      Bank Frick operations (balance, transactions, send)
  crypto    Crypto wallet balance (ETH, SKY)
  mail      Gmail operations (sync, reply)
  journal   Add entries to the journal
